<!--초고층_건물_정보-->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = Skyscraper
| mappings =
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 건물명칭 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =원어건물명칭 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 세계최고층년도 | ontologyProperty = highestBuildingInYear }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 엔지니어 | ontologyProperty = engineer }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 계약자 | ontologyProperty = contractor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 개발사 | ontologyProperty = developer }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 위치 | ontologyProperty = location }}
	{{DateIntervalMapping | templateProperty = 건축기간 | startDateOntologyProperty = buildingStartDate | endDateOntologyProperty = buildingEndDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 완공 | ontologyProperty = buildingEndDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 완공예정 | ontologyProperty = buildingEndDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 개장 | ontologyProperty = openingDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 철거 | ontologyProperty = demolitionDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 파괴 | ontologyProperty = destructionDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 건설비용 | ontologyProperty = cost | unit = Currency }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 연면적 | ontologyProperty = floorArea | unit = Area }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 건축가 | ontologyProperty = architect }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 소유주 | ontologyProperty = owner }}
end}}
